        "A gate receipt may have no Python source only when it is reversible gate safety.",
        "Any other no-source effect is rejected or held as missing parity before ordinary traffic can flip.",
    ],
    classification_meaning: [
        "primary_mutation: the graph write itself, not a side-effect argument",
        "python_parity_effect: existing Python companion behavior that Form must carry before replacing Python",
